#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.167"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.167:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.167:0.2"
msgid "17. Paṭipadāvagga"
msgstr "17. Practice"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: moggallānapaṭipadāsuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.167:0.3"
msgid "167. Mahāmoggallānasutta"
msgstr "167. Moggallāna’s Practice"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.167:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā sāriputto yenāyasmā mahāmoggallāno tenupasaṅkami; "
"upasaṅkamitvā āyasmatā mahāmoggallānena saddhiṃ sammodi."
msgstr ""
"Then Venerable Sāriputta went up to Venerable Mahāmoggallāna, and exchanged "
"greetings with him."

msgctxt "an4.167:1.2"
msgid ""
"Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ "
"nisinno kho āyasmā sāriputto āyasmantaṃ mahāmoggallānaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"When the greetings and polite conversation were over, Sāriputta sat down to "
"one side and said to Mahāmoggallāna:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.167:2.1"
msgid "“Catasso imā, āvuso moggallāna, paṭipadā."
msgstr "“Reverend Moggallāna, there are four ways of practice."

msgctxt "an4.167:2.2"
msgid "Katamā catasso?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.167:2.3"
msgid ""
"Dukkhā paṭipadā dandhābhiññā, dukkhā paṭipadā khippābhiññā, sukhā paṭipadā "
"dandhābhiññā, sukhā paṭipadā khippābhiññā."
msgstr ""
"~Painful practice with slow insight, ~painful practice with swift insight, ~"
"pleasant practice with slow insight, and ~pleasant practice with swift "
"insight."

msgctxt "an4.167:2.4"
msgid "Imā kho, āvuso, catasso paṭipadā."
msgstr "These are the four ways of practice."

#. VAR: catunnaṃ paṭipadānaṃ → catassannaṃ paṭipadānaṃ (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an4.167:2.5"
msgid ""
"Imāsaṃ, āvuso, catunnaṃ paṭipadānaṃ katamaṃ te paṭipadaṃ āgamma anupādāya "
"āsavehi cittaṃ vimuttan”ti?"
msgstr ""
"Which one of these four ways of practice did you rely on to free your mind "
"from defilements by not grasping?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.155"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.167:3.1"
msgid "“Catasso imā, āvuso sāriputta, paṭipadā."
msgstr "“Reverend Sāriputta …"

msgctxt "an4.167:3.2"
msgid "Katamā catasso?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.167:3.3"
msgid ""
"Dukkhā paṭipadā dandhābhiññā, dukkhā paṭipadā khippābhiññā, sukhā paṭipadā "
"dandhābhiññā, sukhā paṭipadā khippābhiññā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.167:3.4"
msgid "Imā kho, āvuso, catasso paṭipadā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.167:3.5"
msgid ""
"Imāsaṃ, āvuso, catunnaṃ paṭipadānaṃ yāyaṃ paṭipadā dukkhā khippābhiññā, imaṃ "
"me paṭipadaṃ āgamma anupādāya āsavehi cittaṃ vimuttan”ti."
msgstr ""
"I relied on the painful practice with swift insight to free my mind from "
"defilements by not grasping.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.167:3.6"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
